<script>
  function getGeoUtil() {
    var TO_MILES = 0.000621371192;
    var TO_RADIANS = Math.PI / 180;
    var TO_DEGREES = 180 / Math.PI;
    var QUARTER_PI = Math.PI / 4;
    var TWO_PI = Math.PI * 2;
    var WGS84 = {
      major: 6378137,
      minor: 6356752.31425,
      flattening: 1 / 298.257223563
    };
    var NO_NAME_PLACE_STRING = "A place with no name";
    var METERS_STRING = "meters";
    var ORIGIN_STRING = "Origin";
    var BODY_CLASSES = {
      noOrigin: "no-origin",
      addDestination: "add-destination"
    };
    var MAP_ELEMENT_CLASS = "mk-map-node-element";
    var MAP_CONTROLS_CLASS = "mk-controls-container";
    var METERS_PER_MILE = 1609.344;
    var DISTANCE_CONVERSION = {
      FeetThreshold: 0.0975,
      MetersPerFoot: 0.3048,
      MetersPerKilometer: 1000,
      MetersPerMile: METERS_PER_MILE,
      MetersThreshold: 0.975,
      MinimumDistance: 1
    };

    function latlongDiff(c1, c2) {
      try {
        return new mapkit.Coordinate(c1.latitude - c2.latitude, c1.longitude - c2.longitude);
      } catch (e) {
        return null;
      }
    }

    function getRelativePointPosition(c1, c2) {
      var diffPoint = latlongDiff(c1, c2);
      if (!diffPoint) {
        return null;
      }
      var qLat = false; qLat = diffPoint.latitude > 0;
      var qLng = false; qLng = diffPoint.longitude > 0;
      if (qLat && !qLng) { //top-left
        return 0;
      } else if (qLat && qLng) { //top-right
        return 1;
      } else if (!qLat && qLng) { //bottom-right
        return 2;
      } else if (!qLat && !qLng) { //bottom-left
        return 3;
      }
      return null;
    }
    function getNearestPointOnViewport(pin, viewportCenter, viewport) {
      console.log('Getting nearest point on viewport', {pin, viewportCenter, viewport});
      var positionWithReferenceToCenter = getRelativePointPosition(pin, viewportCenter);
      var positionWithReferenceToCorner = null;
      if (positionWithReferenceToCenter !== null) {
        positionWithReferenceToCorner = getRelativePointPosition(pin, viewport[positionWithReferenceToCenter]);
      }
      if (positionWithReferenceToCorner === null) {
        console.log('Failed to find Pin quadrant relative to nearest corner');
        return 'Failed to find Pin quadrant relative to nearest corner';
      }
      // check if Pin is inside of the viewport.
      if (positionWithReferenceToCenter === 0 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 2
        || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 1 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 3
        || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 2 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 0
        || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 3 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 1) {
          console.log('Pin is in the viewport');
        return 'Pin is in the viewport';
      }
      // check if Pin is in corners
      if (positionWithReferenceToCenter === positionWithReferenceToCorner) {
        console.log('Pin is on a corner!');
        return viewport[positionWithReferenceToCenter];
      }
      try {
        // find point on north and south edges of viewport
        if (positionWithReferenceToCenter === 0 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 1
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 1 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 0
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 2 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 3
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 3 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 2){
            console.log('D');
          return new mapkit.Coordinate(viewport[positionWithReferenceToCenter].latitude, pin.longitude);
        }
        // find point on east and west edges of viewport
        if (positionWithReferenceToCenter === 0 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 3
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 1 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 2
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 2 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 1
          || positionWithReferenceToCenter === 3 && positionWithReferenceToCorner === 0){
            console.log('E');
          return new mapkit.Coordinate(pin.latitude, viewport[positionWithReferenceToCenter].longitude);
        }
      } catch (e) {
        console.log('Error while finding nearest point on viewport', e);
        return 'Error while finding nearest point on viewport';
      }
      console.log('Failed to find nearest point on viewport');
      return 'Failed to find nearest point on viewport';
    }

    //
    // Adapted from http://www.movable-type.co.uk/scripts/latlong-vincenty.html
    //
    // Geodesic distance calculation using latitude/longitude
    function getGeodesicDistanceInMeters(Coordinate1, Coordinate2) {

      var positions = {
        start: {
          latitude: Coordinate1.latitude * TO_RADIANS,
          longitude: Coordinate1.longitude * TO_RADIANS
        },
        end: {
          latitude: Coordinate2.latitude * TO_RADIANS,
          longitude: Coordinate2.longitude * TO_RADIANS
        }
      };

      var L = positions.end.longitude - positions.start.longitude;
      var tanU1 = (1 - WGS84.flattening) * Math.tan(positions.start.latitude);
      var cosU1 = 1 / Math.sqrt(1 + tanU1 * tanU1);
      var sinU1 = tanU1 * cosU1;
      var tanU2 = (1-WGS84.flattening) * Math.tan(positions.end.latitude);
      var cosU2 = 1 / Math.sqrt(1 + tanU2 * tanU2);
      var sinU2 = tanU2 * cosU2;

      var sin_L, cos_L, sinSqSigma, sinSigma, cosSigma, sigma, sinAlpha, cosSqAlpha, cos2SigmaM, C;

      var _L = L, _Li, iterations = 0;
      do {
        sin_L = Math.sin(_L);
        cos_L = Math.cos(_L);
        sinSqSigma = (cosU2 * sin_L) * (cosU2 * sin_L) +
          (cosU1 * sinU2 - sinU1 * cosU2 * cos_L) *
          (cosU1 * sinU2 - sinU1 * cosU2 * cos_L);
        sinSigma = Math.sqrt(sinSqSigma);
        if (sinSigma === 0) {return 0;}    // co-incident points
        cosSigma = sinU1 * sinU2 + cosU1 * cosU2 * cos_L;
        sigma = Math.atan2(sinSigma, cosSigma);
        sinAlpha = cosU1 * cosU2 * sin_L / sinSigma;
        cosSqAlpha = 1 - sinAlpha * sinAlpha;
        cos2SigmaM = cosSigma - 2 * sinU1 * sinU2 / cosSqAlpha;
        if (isNaN(cos2SigmaM)) {cos2SigmaM = 0;}    // equatorial line: cosSqAlpha=0 (Â§6)
        C = WGS84.flattening / 16 * cosSqAlpha *
          (4 + WGS84.flattening * (4 - 3 * cosSqAlpha));
        _Li = _L;
        _L = L + (1 - C) * WGS84.flattening * sinAlpha * (sigma + C * sinSigma * (cos2SigmaM + C * cosSigma *
          (-1 + 2 * cos2SigmaM * cos2SigmaM)));
      } while (Math.abs(_L - _Li) > 1e-12 && ++iterations < 200)
      if (iterations >= 200) {
        console.log("Warning: Failed to converge");
      }

      var uSq = cosSqAlpha * (WGS84.major * WGS84.major - WGS84.minor * WGS84.minor) /
        (WGS84.minor * WGS84.minor);
      var A = 1 + uSq / 16384 * (4096 + uSq * (-768 + uSq * (320 - 175 * uSq)));
      var B = uSq / 1024 * (256 + uSq * (-128 + uSq * (74 - 47 * uSq)));
      var deltaSigma = B * sinSigma * (cos2SigmaM + B / 4 * (cosSigma * (-1 + 2 * cos2SigmaM *
        cos2SigmaM) - B / 6 * cos2SigmaM * (-3 + 4 * sinSigma * sinSigma) * (-3 + 4 * cos2SigmaM *
        cos2SigmaM)));

      var distanceInMeters = WGS84.minor * A * (sigma - deltaSigma);
      var alpha1 = Math.atan2(cosU2 * sin_L, cosU1 * sinU2 - sinU1 * cosU2 * cos_L);
      var alpha2 = Math.atan2(cosU1 * sin_L, -sinU1 * cosU2 + cosU1 * sinU2 * cos_L);

      alpha1 = (alpha1 + TWO_PI) % TWO_PI; // normalise to 0..360
      alpha2 = (alpha2 + TWO_PI) % TWO_PI; // normalise to 0..360

      return parseInt(distanceInMeters, 10);

    }

    //
    // Meter to Km conversion to be more human readable
    // Lifted from placecard.js
    //

    function convertDistance(distanceMeters, useMetric, metricRatio, nonMetricRatio) {
      return distanceMeters / (useMetric ? metricRatio : nonMetricRatio);
    }

    // Convert and round distance in meters of an ETA value to kilometers or miles depending on the useMetric flag.
    // Distances below 1 km are converted to meters and rounded into units of 50 (e.g. 240m = 250m);
    // distances below 0.1 miles are converted to feet and rounded into units of 50 (e.g. 100m = 350ft);
    // (but distances below 50m/ft are simply rounded (e.g., 11m = 36ft)â€”the minimum distance shown is 1m/ft);
    // distances above 1 km/0.1 mile are rounded to within 1 decimal (e.g. 5240m = 5.2km, 300m = 0.2 miles);
    // distances above 10 km/miles are rounded to the nearest integer (e.g. 13912m = 14km.)
    // Set the smallUnits property of the ETA value to true when using m/ft, and to false for km/miles,
    // and set the roundedDistance property to the distance to be displayed.
    function roundDistance(distanceMeters, useMetric) {
      var roundedDistance = {};
      var convertedDistance = convertDistance(distanceMeters, useMetric, DISTANCE_CONVERSION.MetersPerKilometer, DISTANCE_CONVERSION.MetersPerMile);

      if (convertedDistance < (useMetric ? DISTANCE_CONVERSION.MetersThreshold : DISTANCE_CONVERSION.FeetThreshold)) {
        roundedDistance.smallUnits = true;
        roundedDistance.distance = convertDistance(distanceMeters, useMetric, 1, DISTANCE_CONVERSION.MetersPerFoot);
      } else {
        roundedDistance.smallUnits = false;
        roundedDistance.distance = Math.round(convertedDistance);
      }

      return roundedDistance;
    }

    function distanceUnitLabel(useMetric, roundedDistance) {
      var key = useMetric ?
        (roundedDistance.smallUnits ?
          (roundedDistance.distance === 1 ? "Meter" : "Meters") :
          (roundedDistance.distance === 1 ? "Kilometer" : "Kilometers")) :
        (roundedDistance.smallUnits ?
          (roundedDistance.distance === 1 ? "Foot" : "Feet") :
          (roundedDistance.distance === 1 ? "Mile" : "Miles"));
      return key;
    }

    return {
      getGeodesicDistanceInMeters: getGeodesicDistanceInMeters,
      convertDistance: convertDistance,
      roundDistance: roundDistance,
      distanceUnitLabel: distanceUnitLabel,
      getNearestPointOnViewport: getNearestPointOnViewport
    }
  }
  const geoUtils = getGeoUtil();
</script>

  function updateResultFeatures(feature, viewportCenterCoordinate, viewportCoordinates, deviceLocationCoordinate) {
  
    var coordinate, distanceToViewport, distanceToUser;
    try {
      coordinate = new mapkit.Coordinate(parseFloat(feature.lat), parseFloat(feature.lng));
    } catch (e){}
    feature.centerCoordinate = coordinate;
    feature.distanceToViewport = null;
    feature.distanceToUser = null;
    feature.nearestPointOnViewport = null;
    if (coordinate && viewportCenterCoordinate) {
      console.log('Get nearestPointCoordinate');
      var nearestPointCoordinate = geoUtils.getNearestPointOnViewport(coordinate, viewportCenterCoordinate, viewportCoordinates);
      if (typeof nearestPointCoordinate !== 'string' && nearestPointCoordinate) {
        console.log('nearestPointCoordinate', nearestPointCoordinate);
        feature.nearestPointOnViewport = nearestPointCoordinate;
        distanceToViewport = geoUtils.getGeodesicDistanceInMeters(coordinate, nearestPointCoordinate);
        console.log('distanceToViewport', distanceToViewport);
        feature.distanceToViewport = distanceToViewport / 1000;
      } else {
        feature.error = nearestPointCoordinate;
        if (nearestPointCoordinate === 'Pin is in the viewport') {
          feature.distanceToViewport = 0;
        }
      }
      feature.distanceToViewportWithUnit = feature.distanceToViewport;
      if (feature.distanceToViewport) {
        feature.distanceToViewportWithUnit = `${feature.distanceToViewport} km`;
      }
    }
    if (coordinate && deviceLocationCoordinate) {
      distanceToUser = geoUtils.getGeodesicDistanceInMeters(coordinate, deviceLocationCoordinate);
      feature.distanceToUser = distanceToUser / 1000;
      feature.distanceToUserWithUnit = feature.distanceToUser ? `${feature.distanceToUser} km` : feature.distanceToUser;
    }
    return feature;
  }

<script>
  function getSearchTaskData(task, subtasksByName) {
    const taskData = {
      results: {},
      device: {},
      viewport: {},
      resultList: [],
      country: "",
      viewportTime: 0
    };
    let poiResponses = [];
    let deviceLocationPoint = null;
    let viewportMid = null;
    let viewportCoordinates = null;

    const resultCount = task?.resultSet?.resultList?.length || 0;
    const inputItemMessage = task?.inputItem?.data?.message || {};
    const tartMetadata = task?.inputItem?.data?.tartMetadata || {};
    
    taskData.viewportTime = inputItemMessage.timeSinceMapViewportChanged !== void 0  
      ? inputItemMessage.timeSinceMapViewportChanged 
      : tartMetadata.timeSinceMapViewportChanged;
      
    taskData.country = getCountryFromLocale(task?.inputItem?.data?.header?.locale || "");
    taskData.device.pin = task?.inputItem?.data?.tartMetadata?.deviceLocation || {};

    if (taskData.device.pin.lat !== void 0) { 
      deviceLocationPoint = {
        latitude: parseFloat(taskData.device.pin.lat),
        longitude: parseFloat(taskData.device.pin.lng)
      };
    }

    const mapRegion = task?.inputItem?.data?.tartMetadata?.mapRegion;

    // Adding Viewport
    if (mapRegion) {
      taskData.viewport.mapRegion = mapRegion;
      viewportMid = {
        latitude: (parseFloat(mapRegion.northLat) + parseFloat(mapRegion.southLat)) / 2,
        longitude: (parseFloat(mapRegion.westLng) + parseFloat(mapRegion.eastLng)) / 2
      };
      taskData.viewport.pin = viewportMid;
  
      viewportCoordinates = [
        {latitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.northLat), longitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.westLng)},
        {latitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.northLat), longitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.eastLng)},
        {latitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.southLat), longitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.eastLng)},
        {latitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.southLat), longitude: parseFloat(mapRegion.westLng)}
      ];
      taskData.viewport.regionPoints = viewportCoordinates;
    }

    if (resultCount) {
      console.log('subtasksByName', subtasksByName);
      //task.resultSet.resultList.forEach((result, i)=>{
      subtasksByName['Relevance']?.forEach((result, i)=>{
        let key = result?.data?.surveyKeys['193'];
        let resultValue = result.data.value;
        let {name, address, url, phone, originalCenter, center} = resultValue;
        let poi = { name, address, url, 'telephone': phone, 'place': {'location': originalCenter || center} };
        poiResponses.push(poi);
        let data = {};
        data.index = i;
        data.color = colors[i];
        data.pin = originalCenter || center || {};
        data.poi = poi;
        if (data.pin?.lat) {
          let lat = parseFloat(data.pin.lat)?.toFixed(6);
          let lng = parseFloat(data.pin.lng)?.toFixed(6);
          data.strPinLatLng = `${lat}, ${lng}`;
          data.pin.strLatLng = `${lat}, ${lng}`;
        }
        data.pin = updateResultFeatures(data.pin, viewportMid, viewportCoordinates, deviceLocationPoint);
        
        data.category = null;
        
        if (window.jmespath) {
          let category_en = window.jmespath.search(resultValue, "categories[?level == `2`].localized_name[] | [?!starts_with(not_null(locale, ``), `zh-Hans_CN`)].string_value[] | [0]");
          //console.log('category_en', category_en);
          let category_zh = window.jmespath.search(resultValue, "categories[?level == `4`].localized_name[] | [?starts_with(not_null(locale, ``), `zh-Hans_CN`)].string_value[] | [0]");
          //console.log('category_zh', category_zh);
          data.category = category_en || category_zh;
        }
        
        taskData.results[key] = data;
        taskData.resultList.push(data);
      });

      //console.log('taskData', taskData);
    }

    return taskData;
  }
</script>
<script>
  const task = {% if task %}{{task | json}}{% else %}{}{% endif %};
  const subtasksByName = {% if subtasksByName %}{{subtasksByName | json}}{% else %}{}{% endif %};
  const taskData = getSearchTaskData(task, subtasksByName);
  TaskAPI().updateRating(taskData);
</script>
